<DOCNO> LA100589-0060 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 116334 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 5, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part 6; Page 1; Column 5; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
