MICHAEL EDWARDS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Rolled fillet of sole cooks in the 
same liquid in which carrots and shredded cabbage have been cooked, for a light 
and nutritious meal. Most any seafood or meat can be similarly prepared, if 
wanted. ; Photo, Judith Hurley, co-author of "Healing Foods," writes about 
foods that have curative powers. 
