<P>
Photo, A reader requested the recipe of the lemon-flavored pasta made with 
vodka served at the Gypsy Italian Cafe in Orange, Calif. The alcoholic content 
of vodka in the sauce evaporates upon heating. RANDY LEFFINGWELL / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
