STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EAST GERMANY; WEST GERMANY -- IMMIGRATION; 
CZECHOSLOVAKIA -- TRANSPORTATION; CZECHOSLOVAKIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EAST 
GERMANY 
</P>
